/*
ag-click-active-pseudo

&.ag-click_active の:after疑似要素スタイルを追加する.


```
@include ag-click-active-pseudo($position = relative, $radius = null)
```

Styleguide 1.5.4
*/
ag-click-active-pseudo($position = relative, $radius = null)
  if $position == relative
    &.ag-click_active
      position relative

  &.ag-click_active::after
    content ""
    display block
    position absolute
    top 0
    left 0
    right 0
    bottom 0
    z-index 0
    ag-click-active-base-style()
    
    if $radius
      border-radius $radius